text: RPH may refer to: *Registered Pharmacist (RPh), in the US *Radio Print Handicapped Network, or RPH Australia, a radio reading service network *Royal Perth Hospital, in Australia *Royal Preston Hospital, in England *Roleplaying Heaven World of Warcraft Private server (RPH) on google *a trade name for Tiabendazole *RAGE Plugin Hook, a plugin hook for Grand Theft Auto 5
